Package: tinyslider
Title: Adaptation for R of the 'Tiny-Slider JavaScript' Library
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Etienne",
           family = "Bacher",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "etienne.bacher@protonmail.com")
Description: Provide carousels built with 'Tiny-Slider JavaScript' 
    library. These carousels can be used in 'shiny' applications 
    or interactive R Markdown documents. The user can add HTML cards
    and plots made with 'ggplot2' in the carousel.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: 
    shiny,
    htmlwidgets,
    ggplot2,
    base64enc
Suggests: 
    testthat
URL: https://tinyslider.etiennebacher.com
BugReports: https://github.com/etiennebacher/tinyslider/issues
